Facebook Software Engineering Interview Process
ArticleDuration30 min
Ninja Brown Bag questions
Facebook has quite a thorough interviewer training process. In training, we teach new Facebook interviewers on a set of questions called “Ninja Brown Bag” questions. As a result, these are the most common questions used at Facebook and have the highest frequency of coming up.

Here is a list of the most popular ninja brown bag questions used by Facebook interviewers:

Dictionary Lookup with Wildcard (20 minute question)

https://fellows.pathrise.com/knowledge/guides/problem-dictionary-lookup-with-wildcard

