Other good stuff

Look at the axes: https://fellows.pathrise.com/knowledge/guides/how-tech-companies-evaluate-candidates-on-technical-interviews

The same framework is used at Facebook

Interviewers are trained to leave candidates with a “good experience”. So if you leave feeling like you did well or with a positive experience that doesn’t mean that you passed the hire bar.

